# Guard for build-tarball / dkms_apply_all_patches conditional patch application.
# Format: [!]<relpath-in-tarball>:<grep -E regex>   (ALL lines must hold)
# A leading '!' negates (the pattern must NOT be present).
#
# 0009 is the composed meshstor-main raid variant: it applies only when the
# member-AND helper raid1_can_advertise_p2pdma() (added by the p2pdma-fixes
# feature, commit 0ed31022) is present. On bare upstream `master` the helper is
# absent and 0010 handles the upstream raid shape instead.
raid1-10.c:raid1_can_advertise_p2pdma
